    public class WindowSpecificationImpl
extends TripletImpl
implements WindowSpecification
    An implementation of the model object 'Window Specification'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • FLAGS
    • RES3
    • CFORMAT
    • UBASE
    • XRESOL
    • YRESOL
    • IMGXYRES
    • XLWIND
    • XRWIND
    • YBWIND
